xxl.cursors
Class IteratorEnumeration

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--xxl.cursors.IteratorEnumeration
public class IteratorEnumeration
extends Object
implements Enumeration

The IteratorEnumeration wraps an Iterator to an Enumeration.
Therefore the methods Enumeration.hasMoreElements() and Enumeration.nextElement() have to be implemented.

The implementation is as follows: 


 	public boolean hasMoreElements () {
 		return iterator.hasNext();
 	}
 	public Object nextElement () throws NoSuchElementException {
 		return iterator.next();
 	}
The required functionality is delivered by applying the methods hasNext and next to the given Iterator.
